

Always read AGENTS.md and SYSTEM_CONTEXT.md before writing any code.
Always state which agent you are before starting (@company-graph, @backend-coder, etc.).
Describe your approach and wait for approval before writing code.
Never touch AGENT_OVERRIDES.md.
Never add ollama, proxycurl, or any local LLM.
Use uv for Python deps, pnpm for Node deps.
If a task touches more than 3 files, stop and break it into smaller tasks.
After finishing code, list edge cases and suggest test cases.
When corrected, add a rule to the Persistent Rules section of AGENTS.md.
Run tests before declaring any task complete.